newsitem.title: AUSTRALIA: RTRS-Australian wool indicator steady on 564c/kg.
newsitem.headline: RTRS-Australian wool indicator steady on 564c/kg.

text.p: The Australian eastern wool market eastern indicator was steady on 564 cents a kg clean at sales in Sydney and Melbourne on Tuesday, Wool International (WI) said.
Merino fleece prices were mixed, with 19 micron up to 1.0 percent dearer and 20/21/22m slightly cheaper.
The 23m category was 0.5 percent dearer, 24/26m 0.5 percent cheaper and 25m slightly dearer, WI said.
Merino skirtings were dearer, with 19/21m 0.5 percent dearer and 20m slightly dearer.
